reviews.review_text: the start of the missing 10 years I attended this show and so it began... I got on the bus and didn't get off for 10 years.

Just Lookin' For Their Kites.... Interesting Playin' jam.  Including a couple of definite Dark Star teases... Plus, it sounds like they're going to go back into Terrapin at a couple of points.

This jam alone makes the show worth getting.
good quality audience tape Good quality audience tape  -- no surprise, since the great Charlie Miller is involved.  The band has energy throughout the show.  Cool second set open with Terrapin.
